===Decoration===
In 2002, the national team was honored with the Turkish "[[State Medal of Distinguished Service]]" for their third place achievement at the [[2002 FIFA World Cup]]. All the team members, coaches and officials were given medals.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tccb.gov.tr/ahmet-necdet-sezer-konusmalari/495/56762/a-milli-futbol-takimimiza-devlet-ustun-hizmet-madalyasi-verilmesi-toreni.html|title=Hata Sayfası|website=tccb.gov.tr|access-date=29 October 2016|archive-date=7 July 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150707080130/http://www.tccb.gov.tr/ahmet-necdet-sezer-konusmalari/495/56762/a-milli-futbol-takimimiza-devlet-ustun-hizmet-madalyasi-verilmesi-toreni.html|url-status=live}}</ref>

